{{Quote|Keira and Hayley had the coloring and the look we needed for the tight-knit family. And they take direction well, which is the most important thing.|[[Robin Gurland]], Episode II Casting Director|<ref name="Casting">{{SWArchive|url=episode-ii/bts/production/news20000822.html|text=Casting Update: Son of Local Talent}}</ref>}}
'''Hayley Ann Mooy''' is an Australian former child actress who portrayed [[Pooja Naberrie]] in [[Star Wars: Episode III Revenge of the Sith|''Star Wars'': Episode III ''Revenge of the Sith'']] and a deleted scene of [[Star Wars: Episode II Attack of the Clones|''Star Wars'': Episode II ''Attack of the Clones'']].

